{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"number","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number in E.164 international format.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"number"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates a WhatsApp number with the current device for WhatsApp Business API"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"messaging campaigns. This enables rich messaging with images, documents, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interactive buttons through WhatsApp."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number must be in E.164 international format:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Start with ‘+’ followed by country code"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"No spaces, dashes, or parentheses","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a valid WhatsApp-enabled number"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register WhatsApp during communication preferences setup:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class CommunicationPreferencesManager {","","    struct Preferences {","        var pushEnabled: Bool","        var smsEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappNumber: String?","    }","","    func savePreferences(_ preferences: Preferences) {","        \/\/ Register WhatsApp if user opted in and provided number","        if preferences.whatsappEnabled, let number = preferences.whatsappNumber {","            let normalizedNumber = normalizePhoneNumber(number)","            Pushwoosh.configure.registerWhatsappNumber(normalizedNumber)","        }","","        \/\/ Update channel preferences tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"channel_push\": preferences.pushEnabled,","            \"channel_sms\": preferences.smsEnabled,","            \"channel_whatsapp\": preferences.whatsappEnabled","        ])","    }","","    private func normalizePhoneNumber(_ phone: String) -> String {","        let digits = phone.filter { $0.isNumber }","        return phone.hasPrefix(\"+\") ? \"+\\(digits)\" : \"+\\(digits)\"","    }","}"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerWhatsappNumber:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"registerWhatsappNumber:","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerWhatsappNumber:":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:","title":"registerWhatsappNumber:","abstract":[{"text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging.","type":"text"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration"}}}